    <item>
      <title>毕马威称加拿大首席执行官越来越担心经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ceos-in-canada-are-growing-more-worried-about-growth-kpmg-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毕马威委托进行的一项调查显示，加拿大的首席执行官们对国内经济越来越担忧，但大多数人仍对自己公司未来几年的前景持乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ceos-in-canada-are-growing-more-worried-about-growth-kpmg-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港券商陷入“百年不遇”的股市狂潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hong-kong-brokers-swamped-by-once-in-a-century-stock-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港的股票经纪人正经历职业生涯中最忙碌的时期之一，一位拥有 31 年经验的资深人士将香港股市的突然上涨描述为“百年不遇”的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hong-kong-brokers-swamped-by-once-in-a-century-stock-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大皇家银行分析师称特朗普赢得大选可能利好美国股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/trump-election-sweep-is-bullish-for-us-stocks-rbc-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行资本市场 (RBC Capital Markets) 对分析师的调查显示，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 领导的共和党在选举中大获全胜可能成为对美国股市最为有利的结果，其中能源和金融板块将受益最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/trump-election-sweep-is-bullish-for-us-stocks-rbc-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:55:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度央行委员会提议修改 MIBOR 和新基准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/india-central-bank-panel-moots-changes-to-mibor-new-benchmarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度储备银行设立的一个小组建议改变孟买银行间直接利率（MIBOR）的计算方法，并建议为隔夜货币市场引入新的基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/india-central-bank-panel-moots-changes-to-mibor-new-benchmarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:50:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国乐观情绪抵消地缘政治风险 新兴股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/emerging-stocks-jump-as-china-optimism-offsets-geopolitical-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[发展中国家股市周三上涨，受刺激政策推动的中国股市抵消了中东冲突进一步升级的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/emerging-stocks-jump-as-china-optimism-offsets-geopolitical-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:41:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度 CCI 批准 Mankind Pharma 收购疫苗制造商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/india-s-cci-approves-mankind-pharma-s-purchase-of-vaccine-maker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据印度竞争委员会发布的消息，印度反垄断监管机构批准 Mankind Pharma Ltd. 以 1363 亿卢比（16 亿美元）收购疫苗制造商 Bharat Serums and Vaccines Ltd.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/india-s-cci-approves-mankind-pharma-s-purchase-of-vaccine-maker</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗大规模导弹袭击进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射了约 200 枚弹道导弹后，本杰明内塔尼亚胡誓言要对伊朗进行报复，这是两国之间敌对行动的严重升级，世界大国担心这可能演变成一场中东战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:06:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗袭击进行报复，油价继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射约 200 枚弹道导弹，导致以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡誓言进行报复，并加大了该地区原油供应的风险，油价连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市持稳，焦急等待以色列回应：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东局势紧张，市场进入观望状态，股市小幅波动，债券市场趋于稳定。油价上涨，黄金价格徘徊在历史高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:39:40 GMT</pubDate>
